你能够调用以下的API:
[['QuantInvestmentResearch.find_papers', {'name': 'QuantInvestmentResearch.find_papers', 'description': 'This function searches for research papers on quantitative investing based on a specified topic and returns a specified number of results.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'count', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of papers to return.'}, {'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the research papers.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'papers', 'description': 'A list of up to the specified number of research papers on the topic.'}]}], ['QuantInvestmentFunds.get_performance_data', {'name': 'QuantInvestmentFunds.get_performance_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves performance data for quantitative investment funds based on a specified strategy and returns a specified number of results.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'strategy', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The investment strategy of the funds.'}, {'name': 'count', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of funds to return.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'funds', 'description': 'A list of up to the specified number of quantitative investment funds with their performance data.'}]}], ['AlgorithmTradingTrends.get_analysis_articles', {'name': 'AlgorithmTradingTrends.get_analysis_articles', 'description': 'This function searches for analysis articles on algorithm trading trends based on a specified keyword and returns a specified number of results.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'count', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of articles to return.'}, {'name': 'keyword', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The keyword to search for in the articles.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'articles', 'description': 'A list of up to the specified number of analysis articles on algorithm trading trends.'}]}], ['QuantInvestmentAdvice.get_investment_tips', {'name': 'QuantInvestmentAdvice.get_investment_tips', 'description': 'This function provides investment tips for quantitative investment funds based on a specified fund type and returns a specified number of results.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'fundType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of investment funds.'}, {'name': 'count', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of tips to return.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'tips', 'description': 'A list of up to the specified number of investment tips for the specified type of funds.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `QuantInvestmentResearch.find_papers` 并传入 `count` 和 `topic`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "QuantInvestmentResearch.find_papers",
    "args": "{'count': 3, 'topic': 'quantitative investing'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
